+# CRITICAL: Changes Are NOT on Server Yet!
+
+## Current Situation:
+- ✓ Fixes are committed locally (2 commits ahead)
+- ✗ Changes NOT pushed to GitHub
+- ✗ Server still has OLD code with bugs
+
+## The Fix:
+Changed delete buttons to pass `slug` instead of `id` because:
+- State model uses `getRouteKeyName() = 'slug'`
+- Category model uses `getRouteKeyName() = 'slug'`  
+- Routes use `{state}` and `{category}` which Laravel resolves by the route key
+- Old code passed numeric ID → 404 error
+- New code passes slug → works correctly
+
+## Example:
+- OLD (broken): `/admin/states/2` → 404
+- NEW (works): `/admin/states/arunachal-pradesh` → ✓
+
+## Deploy Steps:
+
+### Option 1: Push from local machine (if you have GitHub access)
+```bash
+cd govt-job-portal-new
+git push origin main
+```
+
+Then on server:
+```bash
+cd /var/www/jobone
+git pull origin main
+php artisan view:clear
+sudo systemctl restart php8.2-fpm
+```
+
+### Option 2: Manual file upload to server
+Upload these 2 files to server:
+1. `resources/views/admin/categories/index.blade.php`
+2. `resources/views/admin/states/index.blade.php`
+
+Then on server:
+```bash
+cd /var/www/jobone
+php artisan view:clear
+sudo systemctl restart php8.2-fpm
+```
+
+### Option 3: Direct edit on server
+SSH to server and edit the files directly:
+
+```bash
+cd /var/www/jobone
+
+# Edit states view
+nano resources/views/admin/states/index.blade.php
+# Change line 140: onclick="confirmDeleteState({{ $st->id }})"
+# To: onclick="confirmDeleteState('{{ $st->slug }}')"
+# Change line 174: function confirmDeleteState(id) {
+# To: function confirmDeleteState(slug) {
+
+# Edit categories view  
+nano resources/views/admin/categories/index.blade.php
+# Change line 157: onclick="confirmDeleteCategory({{ $cat->id }})"
+# To: onclick="confirmDeleteCategory('{{ $cat->slug }}')"
+# Change line 195: function confirmDeleteCategory(id) {
+# To: function confirmDeleteCategory(slug) {
+
+# Clear cache and restart
+php artisan view:clear
+sudo systemctl restart php8.2-fpm
+```
+
+## Test After Deploy:
+1. Go to https://jobone.in/admin/states
+2. Click delete on any state
+3. Check browser console - form action should be like `/admin/states/karnataka` (not `/admin/states/11`)
+4. Submit - should work without 404
+
+## Files Changed:
+- resources/views/admin/categories/index.blade.php (line 157, 195)
+- resources/views/admin/states/index.blade.php (line 140, 174)
